    <p>The <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Dashboard-as-a-student/ta-p/512" target="_blank">Card View Dashboard </a>displays favorite courses. Â If you can't view your courses on your Canvas Dashboard, you may need to favorite the course in your Courses list.</p>
<p>If your Courses list does not display your course, talk to your instructor or your institution's Canvas Admin for assistance.</p>
<p><strong>Notes: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>When no courses are <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-customize-my-Courses-list-as-a-student/ta-p/500" target="_blank">favorited</a>, the courses list automatically displays up to 20 courses alphabetically in the drop-down menu.</li>
<li>If your Dashboard looks different than what is displayed in this lesson, your institution may be using Canvas for Elementary in your course. Learn how to navigate around <a href="/t5/Canvas-for-Elementary-Student/How-do-I-navigate-my-subject-as-a-student/ta-p/493134" target="_blank">Subjects</a> and <a href="/t5/Canvas-for-Elementary-Student/How-do-I-use-my-Homeroom-as-a-student/ta-p/494118" target="_blank">Homeroom</a>. </li>
</ul>
